{"type":"text","timestamp":1780728159692,"sessionID":"ses_16456759bffexNlpdmr83lyyd3","part":{"id":"prt_e9bab4552001P411uizsMv0LD5","messageID":"msg_e9bab3a1b001u45dP7svUiw42g","sessionID":"ses_16456759bffexNlpdmr83lyyd3","type":"text","text":"The SQL shows archive is status-only, soft-delete uses `deleted_at`, and purge is a bounded hard-delete after retention. I’m checking fanout/audit creation and settings snapshot before finalizing transfer judgments.","time":{"start":1780728153426,"end":1780728159690},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0d3203d123fc9203016a23c159648c819182f58ea09b5d4618","phase":"commentary"}}}}
